items.title: Verlander goes for clincher in Astros home debut
items.summary: The energy level should be electric and the excitement off the charts at Minute Maid Park on Sunday, when Justin Verlander makes his Astros home debut with the chance to deliver the American League West title to Houston.
items.content: The energy level should be electric and the excitement off the charts at Minute Maid Park on Sunday, when Justin Verlander makes his Astros home debut with the chance to deliver the American League West title to Houston.

items.title: Managers Postgame: Black on Rockies' rout
items.summary: Bud Black's Rockies scored 16 runs and didn't give up any to improve their hold on the second NL Wild Card.
